description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Fireworks filling the Tokyo Night Sky
-Shirakawa-go, the World Heritage Site in Japan
-Grand-Place, Belgium in Winter
-Fireworks in the Sky
-Starry Sky and Colosseum
-Fireworks Display
-Night View of Hong Kong
-Night View of Jiufen, Taiwan
-Lantern Festival in Vietnam
-Sunset at the Tokyo Waterfront
name: Fireworks and Nightscape
